@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fsovmr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v0
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.exp(wp.exp(v0 + 0.18)))
    v1 = v0
    v0 = wp.abs(0.63)
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.abs(tmp + 0.03) / v0))
    v0 = (wp.cos(v0) - wp.cos(wp.cos(v1 + 0.28)))
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.sin(tmp + 0.62) - wp.abs(v2 + 0.41)))
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.sin(v1 + 0.41) - v2))
    data[tid] = v0
